divs: sighting detailson my way home from work i notice in the north east sky just above the tree line very bright lights, as bright as venus would be in the sky. i only saw it shortly since i was driving, but it looked like a pair of lights almost on top of each other similar to what headlights look like from a distance. it\they did not appear to be moving at all. i lost it behind trees as i drove.
